{"text_id":155354,"tokens":["The"," importance"," of"," summer"," projects"," in"," high"," school"," cannot"," be"," over","stated","."," These"," projects"," not"," only"," help"," students"," retain"," and"," apply"," knowledge"," acquired"," during"," the"," academic"," year",","," but"," also"," foster"," critical"," thinking",","," creativity",","," and"," time"," management"," skills","."," As","signing"," summer"," projects"," by"," course"," instructors"," is"," crucial"," to"," ensure"," that"," students"," meet"," the"," expectations"," of"," the"," course"," and"," develop"," a"," deeper"," understanding"," of"," the"," subject"," matter","."," A"," thorough"," prompt",","," clear"," instructions",","," and"," a"," specific"," rubric"," are"," essential"," to"," guide"," students"," in"," completing"," a"," project"," that"," meets"," the"," course","'","s"," objectives",".","\n\n","As","signing"," summer"," projects"," by"," instructors"," has"," several"," benefits","."," Firstly",","," it"," allows"," students"," to"," delve"," deeper"," into"," a"," topic"," that"," they"," may"," have"," briefly"," touched"," upon"," during"," the"," academic"," year","."," This"," helps"," to"," reinforce"," learning"," and"," solidify"," understanding",","," making"," it"," more"," likely"," that"," students"," will"," retain"," information"," over"," the"," summer"," break","."," Secondly",","," instructor","-","assigned"," projects"," provide"," students"," with"," a"," sense"," of"," direction"," and"," structure",","," enabling"," them"," to"," stay"," focused"," and"," motivated","."," This"," is"," particularly"," important"," for"," high"," school"," students",","," who"," may"," lack"," the"," discipline"," and"," self","-","motivation"," to"," engage"," in"," self","-","directed"," learning",".","\n\n","On"," the"," other"," hand",","," allowing"," students"," to"," create"," their"," own"," summer"," projects"," can"," have"," drawbacks","."," Without","